TI End-to-End Optimization for a Compact Optical Neural Network Based on
   Nanostructured 2 x 2 Optical Processors
SO IEEE PHOTONICS JOURNAL
LA English
DT Article
DE Optical network units; Optical computing; Nonlinear optics; Program
