TI Multi-wavelength diffractive optical neural network integrated with 2D
   photonic crystals for joint optical classification
SO NANOPHOTONICS
LA English
DT Article
DE optical computing; optical machine learning; optical neural network;
   diffractive deep neural network; multi-wavelength parallelism; 2D
