SO IEEE PHOTONICS JOURNAL
LA English
DT Article
DE Optical logic gates; I/Q modulator; direct detection
ID HIGHLY NONLINEAR FIBER; HIGH-SPEED; XOR; TRANSMISSION; SIGNALS;
